  <brief_title>Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction After Propofol Anesthesia for Noncardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>POCD ELA</acronym>
  <official_title>Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction After Intravenous Anesthesia or Closed-loop Coadministration of Propofol and Remifentanil Guided by Bispectral Index for Noncardiac Surgery : a Randomized Monocenter Study</official_title>
